<item>
            <title>[SPARK-39216] Do not collapse projects in CombineUnions if it hasCorrelatedSubquery</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-39216</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-37915&quot; title=&quot;Combine unions if there is a project between them&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPARK-37915&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPARK-37915&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; added CollapseProject in rule CombineUnions, but it shouldn&apos;t collapse projects that contain correlated subqueries since haven&apos;t been de-correlated (PullupCorrelatedPredicates).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is a simple example to reproduce this issue&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
SELECT (SELECT IF(x, 1, 0)) AS a
FROM (SELECT &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;) t(x)
UNION 
SELECT 1 AS a &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Exception:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
java.lang.IllegalStateException: Couldn&apos;t find x#4 in [] &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
